T16TD4415E:350a-1: ratna tri sva sti g'a th'a /
T16TD4415E:350a-3: dkon mchog gsum gyi bkra shis kyi tshigs su bcad pa /
T16TD4415E:350a-4: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
T16TD4415E:350a-5: bde gshegs rgyal ba gang gi mthu nyid kyis /
T16TD4415E:350a-6: legs pa'i 'khor los sgyur rgyal las byung ba'i //
T16TD4415E:350a-7: sku gsum mngon par mtho ba'i bkra shis gang //
T16TD4415E:350a-8: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog / zhi ba chags med dam chos nor bu 'dra //
T16TD4415E:350a-9: legs par bshad pa las byung bkra shis dang //
T16TD4415E:350a-10: bdud rtsi lta bur gsungs pa'i bkra shis gang //
T16TD4415E:350a-11: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog / thugs rje che las mngon byung byang chub sems //
T16TD4415E:350a-12: mngon par mtho ba 'khor ba'i sa rab non //
T16TD4415E:350a-13: stobs ldan dge 'dun dag gi bkra shis gang //
T16TD4415E:350a-14: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog / dkon mchog gsum gyi bkra shis kyi tshigs su bcad pa rdzogs so /
